---
// src/components/FaqSection.astro
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen bg-black py-32 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden font-sans selection:bg-gray-800 selection:text-gray-300">
  
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-white/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-12 md:gap-8 mb-24">
      
      <div class="md:w-[55%]">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-300 uppercase mb-8">
          <span>05</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span>
          <span>FAQ</span>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-[44px] md:text-[56px] leading-[1.1] font-serif text-gray-300 tracking-tight">
          Preparing for liftoff
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-[40%] pt-2 md:pt-14">
        <p class="text-[20px] md:text-[22px] leading-relaxed font-serif text-gray-300 opacity-90">
          Everything you need to know before launching your hackathon project.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="w-full border-t border-dashed border-gray-800">
      
      <details class="group border-b border-dashed border-gray-800">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-8 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-900 px-4 -mx-4 transition-colors rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-serif text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors pr-8">
            Who can participate in AstroHack?
          </h3>
          <div class="relative w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[1.5px] bg-current transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1.5px] h-full bg-current transition-all duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 group-open:opacity-0"></div>
          </div>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-8 -mx-4 text-gray-300 font-sans text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed opacity-0 -translate-y-2 group-open:opacity-100 group-open:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
          AstroHack is open to all university students! Whether you're a full-stack web developer building telemetry dashboards, or an aspiring data scientist training AI models on satellite imagery, there's a place for your crew.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group border-b border-dashed border-gray-800">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-8 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-900 px-4 -mx-4 transition-colors rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-serif text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors pr-8">
            Do I need previous aerospace experience?
          </h3>
          <div class="relative w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[1.5px] bg-current transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1.5px] h-full bg-current transition-all duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 group-open:opacity-0"></div>
          </div>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-8 -mx-4 text-gray-300 font-sans text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed opacity-0 -translate-y-2 group-open:opacity-100 group-open:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
          Not at all. We provide the space APIs, orbital datasets, and expert mentors. You just need to bring your programming skills—whether that's JavaScript, Python, or anything in between—and a passion for the cosmos.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group border-b border-dashed border-gray-800">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-8 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-900 px-4 -mx-4 transition-colors rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-serif text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors pr-8">
            What kind of projects can we build?
          </h3>
          <div class="relative w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[1.5px] bg-current transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1.5px] h-full bg-current transition-all duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 group-open:opacity-0"></div>
          </div>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-8 -mx-4 text-gray-300 font-sans text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed opacity-0 -translate-y-2 group-open:opacity-100 group-open:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
          Anything software-related that solves a space problem! Past projects include AI-driven rover navigation systems, MERN-stack mission control interfaces, and real-time orbital debris tracking algorithms.
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="group border-b border-dashed border-gray-800">
        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center py-8 cursor-pointer list-none hover:bg-gray-900 px-4 -mx-4 transition-colors rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-[20px] md:text-[22px] font-serif text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors pr-8">
            How do teams and submissions work?
          </h3>
          <div class="relative w-4 h-4 text-gray-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[1.5px] bg-current transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1.5px] h-full bg-current transition-all duration-300 group-open:rotate-90 group-open:opacity-0"></div>
          </div>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-8 -mx-4 text-gray-300 font-sans text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed opacity-0 -translate-y-2 group-open:opacity-100 group-open:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-300">
          You can work solo or in teams of up to 4. Projects must be built during the 48-hour window and deployed live (using platforms like Vercel or Render) for the judges to evaluate your final repository.
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Import Playfair Display for the elegant serif headings */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&display=swap');

  .font-serif {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  /* Hide the default HTML details marker arrow */
  details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
</style>